forms major scoring duty via isolation, White is more of a premium role player who does a bit of everything on both offense and defense.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1986, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"score\": 0.998745339577846, \"rank\": 0.0011133355675845835, \"text\": \"White\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He averaged 15.2 points, 5.2 assists and 1.2 blocks per game during the regular season.\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2170, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am happy to announce that Derrick will compete at his first Olympic Games on the heels of a championship season in Boston,\\\" USA Basketball managing director Grant Hill said.\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2290, \"end\": 2296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7131840599737388e-20, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\"}, {\"begin\": 2332, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5565590596910977e-30, \"text\": \"Grant Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We look forward to him joining the team in the coming days as we continue preparations for Paris.\\\"\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2441, \"end\": 2446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998930954973, \"rank\": 1.06904433426135e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\",